    "=============================================================================\n",
    "CORRIDOR ORIGIN ANALYSIS\n",
    "=============================================================================\n",
    "Kitsap Transit — StreetLight Data\n",


    "Traffic patterns originating from commercial corridors using StreetLight with 2024 data \n",
    "COmmerciial zone originations. Produces:\n",
    "  - Volume heatmaps by corridor, hour, and day type\n",
    "  - Trip length distributions (local vs. pass-through)\n",
    "  - Speed patterns as a congestion proxy\n",
    "  - Corridor typology classification\n",
    "  - Service hour gap inventory (volume only — not demand confirmation)\n",
    "\n",
    "NOTE: This analysis characterizes existing vehicle movement from StreetLight\n",
    "estimated trip counts.  Gaps identified as\n",
    "occurring outside transit service hours represent periods of vehicle movement\n",
    "without coverage — not validated ridership potential. No recommendation for\n",
    "new or expanded service should be drawn from this script alone.\n",

   ]
